'''Orange-frilled mushrooms''' were native to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Felucia/Legends|Felucia]]. This [[Mushroom/Legends|mushroom]] grew to be at least fifteen feet tall. It was a partially-transparent [[orange]] color and it had transparent vines hanging off its dome. It lived among many other types of [[Fungus/Legends|fungi]] on Felucia.

